University relationsBold ideas. New perspectives. Recent graduates bring more than an education to the table; they bring a passion for their work. And that can truly change the world.At IHS Markit, we look to leading academic institutions, so we can empower future leaders like you to collaborate with our global teams, discover the high science behind IHS Markit products, develop ideas and then run with them.Learn more about internships, apprenticeships and career development.Attention students and other job seekers:

