Markit

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

For the villages in Iran, see Markit, Iran.

Markit Ltd.





Type

Public


Traded as
NASDAQ: MRKT


Industry
Financial services


Fate
in 2016 merged with IHS Inc. to form IHS Markit


